===Noun===
'''bodhisattva''' (''plural'' '''bodhisattvas''')
#The [[Shakyamuni]] [[Buddha]], as he was before his enlightenment in [[nirvana]].
#In [[Mahayana]] [[Buddhism]], any being who has forestalled their [[enlightenment]] until they have completed a vow to bring all other beings into nirvana.
#In [[Theravada]] Buddhism, the Buddha [[Maitreya]], from now until his enlightenment.

====Etymology====
From the [[Sanskrit]], meaning "enlightening-being"

